comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Vulnerabilities were found fuzzing `mbox_from_parse`\n\nDifferent inputs reproducing the behavior are\n```\n0xe7,0xdf,0x1,0x0,0x30,0x3f,0x20,0x32,0x20,0x30,0x3a,0x32,0x39,0x20,0x3f,0x3f,0x3f,0x20,0x34,0x39,0x30,0x34,0xdb,0x32,0x32,0x3a,0x32,0x36,\n0x20,0x32,0x20,0x56,0x3f,0x3f,0x3f,0x3f,0x20,0x33,0x20,0x32,0x30,0x3a,0x32,0x30,0x3a,0x32,0x32,0x20,0x2d,0x32,\n0x20,0xff,0xf6,0xff,0xff,0x3f,0x3f,0x3f,0x20,0x34,0x20,0x32,0x34,0x3a,0x32,0x34,0x3a,0x32,0x34,0x20,0x32,0x34,\n```\n\nPatch could be adding checks with regards to `msg_end` \n```\ndiff --git a/src/lib-mail/mbox-from.c b/src/lib-mail/mbox-from.c\nindex 452e32ea02..46e0a27ab1 100644\n--- a/src/lib-mail/mbox-from.c\n+++ b/src/lib-mail/mbox-from.c\n@@ -188,8 +188,8 @@ int mbox_from_parse(const unsigned char *msg, size_t size,\n        /* optional named timezone */\n        if (alt_stamp)\n                ;\n-       else if (!i_isdigit(msg[0]) || !i_isdigit(msg[1]) ||\n-                !i_isdigit(msg[2]) || !i_isdigit(msg[3])) {\n+       else if (msg_end \u003e msg+3 \u0026\u0026 ( !i_isdigit(msg[0]) || !i_isdigit(msg[1]) ||\n+                !i_isdigit(msg[2]) || !i_isdigit(msg[3]))) {\n                /* skip to next space */\n                while (msg \u003c msg_end \u0026\u0026 *msg != ' ') {\n                        if (*msg == '\\r' || *msg == '\\n')\n@@ -199,7 +199,7 @@ int mbox_from_parse(const unsigned char *msg, size_t size,\n                if (msg+5 \u003e msg_end)\n                        return -1;\n                msg++;\n-       } else if ((msg[0] == '-' || msg[0] == '+') \u0026\u0026\n+       } else if (msg_end \u003e msg+5 \u0026\u0026 (msg[0] == '-' || msg[0] == '+') \u0026\u0026\n                   i_isdigit(msg[1]) \u0026\u0026 i_isdigit(msg[2]) \u0026\u0026\n                   i_isdigit(msg[3]) \u0026\u0026 i_isdigit(msg[4]) \u0026\u0026 msg[5] == ' ') {\n                /* numeric timezone, use it */\n@@ -212,13 +212,13 @@ int mbox_from_parse(const unsigned char *msg, size_t size,\n \n        if (!alt_stamp) {\n                /* year */\n-               if (mbox_parse_year(msg, \u0026tm) \u003c 0)\n+               if (msg + 4 \u003c msg_end \u0026\u0026 mbox_parse_year(msg, \u0026tm) \u003c 0)\n                        return -1;\n                msg += 4;\n        }\n \n        tm.tm_isdst = -1;\n-       if (!seen_timezone \u0026\u0026 msg != msg_end \u0026\u0026\n+       if (!seen_timezone \u0026\u0026 msg + 5 \u003c msg_end \u0026\u0026\n            msg[0] == ' ' \u0026\u0026 (msg[1] == '-' || msg[1] == '+') \u0026\u0026\n            i_isdigit(msg[2]) \u0026\u0026 i_isdigit(msg[3]) \u0026\u0026\n            i_isdigit(msg[4]) \u0026\u0026 i_isdigit(msg[5])) {\n```\n\n## Impact\n\nA buffer over read may result in sensitive data leak, or in a crash if it accesses another memory page\n\nI am not sure if the impact is security sensitive, so I preferred to report it here first","bounty_amount":"50.0","formatted_bounty":"$50","weakness":{"id":9,"name":"Buffer Over-read"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":null,"vote_count":2,"voters":["since2003","dolph1n"],"severity":{"rating":"none","score":0.0,"author_type":"Team","metrics":{"attack_vector":"network","attack_complexity":"low","privileges_required":"low","user_interaction":"none","scope":"unchanged","confidentiality":"none","integrity":"none","availability":"none"}},"structured_scope":{"databaseId":42899,"asset_type":"SOURCE_CODE","asset_identifier":"https://github.com/dovecot/core","max_severity":"critical"},"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"activities":[{"id":7501988,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Hi! Thanks for reporting this, we'll take a look.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2020-04-01T09:07:02.227Z","updated_at":"2020-04-01T09:07:02.227Z","